[normal]In addition to bridges and underpasses[bold] [bold]what other cost-effective measures can be introduced to replace or improve safety at level crossings?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]How should expenditure on improving safety at level crossings be prioritised in relation to other demands on the rail budget?[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
